    "role": "Unit test suite for the agent-instructions synchronization utility module.",
    "responsibilities": [
      "Verify that syncAgentInstructionsFile and related sync functions correctly write agent instructions, git attributes, git ignore, search ignore, and spine ignore files into a repository.",
